\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {12}{\ignorespaces Parameter-identification history for the dense torus benchmark. The plot shows the relative errors of $\mu $ and $K$ together with the traction-mismatch trace recorded during optimization. The figure supports the benchmark claim in the text: under known kinematics, the inverse trajectory is stable, the parameters converge rapidly into the correct regime, and the traction mismatch decreases to the $10^{-8}$ loss level by the end of the run.\relax }}{26}{figure.caption.46}\protected@file@percent }
